{
  "stem": "17426.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 315.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I went to my brother and I ask him to join us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he didn't know how to swim.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we were each to our own fate, left to whatever we could do to survive, to rescue.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I lowered myself with this friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as I lowered myself, others seeing this also lowered themself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by the time there was seven or eight or nine or 10, the rope unwound and broke.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we all were in the deep of the North Sea.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Many of us didn't come up more than once or twice, just to gulp a-- a bit of air and went down again.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I held on to the side of the boat with my hands and my knees, and crawled-- I knew that I could not swim away from here.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Until I went to the back of the boat where the draft wasn't.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And at that point, I saw a piece of deck that was swimming several feet from me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said to myself, that's where I am going to swim over to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I'm going to put it under my chest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it's either going to go down with me, or I survive it-- or will survive with me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so I swam over and I started to-- I put it under my chest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I started to swim away, paddle away with my legs and feet as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Until I went just about, I would say, about a half-- half the length of a football field.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "About 50 yards.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there, I saw a small boat crossing from the northeast to the southwest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Small boat.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was only a little point at first.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
